summary: Emilia Clarke Should Never Try To Imitate Chewbacca Ever Again
title: Emilia Clarke Should Never Try To Imitate Chewbacca Ever Again
body:
We now know an acting gig for which Emilia Clarke is eminently unqualified: Wookiee impressionist.

Clarke, who plays Qi’ra in “Solo: A Star Wars Story,” attempted her best Chewbacca at the behest of Jimmy Fallon on “The Tonight Show” Monday. The host fed her lines in English that Clarke was supposed to translate into Chewie’s tongue.

The “Game of Thrones” star failed, hilariously.
